  "description": "<p>阿波罗宇航员、登月第二人奥尔德林（Buzz Aldrin）呼吁全世界<a href=\"http://cn.nytimes.com/opinion/20130629/c29aldrin/\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">联合开发月球</span></a>， 认为第二次“登月竞赛”是一个死胡同，美国应作为这一全球开发月球行动的领导者制定路线。<strong>奥尔德林建议，首先缔造一个国际月球发展合作组织。他设想了一个 全面的计划，让火星在今后25年内出现人类的永久性定居点。</strong></p><img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://cnbeta.feedsportal.com/c/34306/f/624776/s/2e09f52d/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /><div class=\"mf-viral\"><table border=\"0\"><tr><td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/twitter/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F243065.htm&amp;t=%E5%A5%A5%E5%B0%94%E5%BE%B7%E6%9E%97%E5%91%BC%E5%90%81%E8%81%94%E5%90%88%E5%BC%80%E5%8F%91%E6%9C%88%E7%90%83\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/twitter.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/facebook/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F243065.htm&amp;t=%E5%A5%A5%E5%B0%94%E5%BE%B7%E6%9E%97%E5%91%BC%E5%90%81%E8%81%94%E5%90%88%E5%BC%80%E5%8F%91%E6%9C%88%E7%90%83\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/facebook.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/linkedin/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F243065.htm&amp;t=%E5%A5%A5%E5%B0%94%E5%BE%B7%E6%9E%97%E5%91%BC%E5%90%81%E8%81%94%E5%90%88%E5%BC%80%E5%8F%91%E6%9C%88%E7%90%83\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/linkedin.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/gplus/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F243065.htm&amp;t=%E5%A5%A5%E5%B0%94%E5%BE%B7%E6%9E%97%E5%91%BC%E5%90%81%E8%81%94%E5%90%88%E5%BC%80%E5%8F%91%E6%9C%88%E7%90%83\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/googleplus.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/email/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F243065.htm&amp;t=%E5%A5%A5%E5%B0%94%E5%BE%B7%E6%9E%97%E5%91%BC%E5%90%81%E8%81%94